message:
In-depth look at human trafficking in Alabama. NGOs and LE working hard! 
“For years, it wasn’t deemed trafficking -it was deemed prostitution,” Caffery said. “I hate that word- no 11-year-old, no 16-year-old decides they want to be a prostitute.” https://buff.ly/2tAWp0G
